{"tid":261864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【生死有命】男子開槍自轟頭唔死 子彈穿頭射入女友胸口身亡","createTime":"2017-05-28T19:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T21:14:08.000Z","uid":14600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bde6693b29c87c4ba2db382ce3c4f15455688da","tid":261864,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170529&amp;guid=56753008&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170529%26guid%3D56753008%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=K2rtsnVmT241f0JEEC8jSDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e42fd2ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170529%26guid%3D56753008%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=45a24466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170529&amp;guid=56753008&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n美國阿拉斯加州一名男子疑開槍向頭部自轟，豈料子彈穿過他頭骨，打中22歲女友胸口，女友最後重傷不治，男子卻活了下來，他現被控二級謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n案發在上月19日凌晨，檢察官指21歲的西布森（Victor Sibson）向自己頭部開槍時，與他拍拖多年的女朋友、22歲的哈格（Brittanymae Haag）企圖阻止，豈料子彈穿過西布森的頭部後打中哈格。救護員發現哈格時，她躺在地上胸口大量出血，兩人隨即被送院搶救，西布森頭部受傷、撿回一命，哈格卻傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n西布森曾向探員透露，不記得自己曾經開槍。戴著保護頭盔的他上周二出庭，否認控罪。他在庭上向法官表示自己失業，沒錢聘請代表律師，「我們能否今天就決定我是否有罪？」<br />\n<br />\n由於他未能交出25萬美元（195萬港元）保釋金，目前被還柙，等候8月21日再應訊，一旦他被定罪，最高刑罰為監禁99年。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司/英國《都市報》"},{"pid":"d6b39eb58532d232cc4e6f739681f587539eaaff","tid":261864,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1cb2053248751c27d5dce41e192574f3f8a08d3","tid":261864,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:14:43.000Z","msg":"其實點解外國咁鐘意判咁多年監 唔直接判終身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0441f0bafdcee554b8c3f44d89da35450a76b5","tid":261864,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:18:23.000Z","msg":"又唔係蓄意有預謀，又唔係死一大班人，99年&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"84c64292ca1b381e1613601da2bbbaeaeec764d3","tid":261864,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:25:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75438095f3a5dfdb4638991530f1f6ae6cff0387","tid":261864,"uid":53836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca73cd7fe8e998ba7cc2ac4431ba7d71d18f006b","tid":261864,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bbb820b9901c29b0548aaaf954c0f5ece9ec93a","tid":261864,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:51:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbfa4a8a9660c0f362a0fc85014359ecb5005b7c","tid":261864,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:58:37.000Z","msg":"子彈穿過心口，再進入頭部，<br />\n佢都係冇受傷架"},{"pid":"8243312610c9bbd38f6c59a4f3c61ff1e3ad8161","tid":261864,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:01:23.000Z","msg":"新古惑的槍"},{"pid":"f81967fb8ddc04b742008587a3cabc42ffa4d0cb","tid":261864,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:03:55.000Z","msg":"中頭都無事<br />\n有無子彈路徑圖？"},{"pid":"57ad4210f39c365441c2bfe71ee5b716ec75b761","tid":261864,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時真係唔到你唔信邪"},{"pid":"d03aa7c1112ee225ddfe43c5d862d392531c40e7","tid":261864,"uid":41551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>子彈穿過心口，再進入頭部，<br />\n佢都係冇受傷架</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ead2ccd6c6be074014569e33c6eb5ce7ee4c2c2","tid":261864,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"點改謀殺<br />\n<br />\n最多咪誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c151cfe946795282147b0a7ec53139267b557f16","tid":261864,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點判謀殺<br />\n<br />\n最多咪誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"57be8c74f6b1160b142333dba0d3019876175748","tid":261864,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T21:14:08.000Z","msg":"肥屍大隻中心口就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}